335
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:32,880
It's useless now.

336
00:18:33,790 --> 00:18:34,440
Go ahead.

337
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:39,640
Officer,

338
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:42,230
