They'll be fine.

415
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:57,320
They won't have any issues.

416
00:24:57,750 --> 00:24:58,610
What about you?

417
00:25:01,170 --> 00:25:02,700
Will you have any problems?

418
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:05,520
I won't.

419
00:25:08,830 --> 00:25:09,830
How much farther?

