00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,760
Where are you?

428
00:25:52,070 --> 00:25:53,390
What's wrong?

429
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:54,640
Captain Zhou,

430
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,300
