448
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,090
for him in that room.

449
00:29:49,440 --> 00:29:50,900
Qu Tong also stayed there?

450
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,000
Qu Tong came the day before yesterday.

451
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:54,980
Xiaowei told her to sleep

452
00:29:54,980 --> 00:29:56,640
on the sofa in the living room.

453
00:29:58,680 --> 00:29:59,880
You're quite honest.

454
00:30:03,270 --> 00:30:04,880
When the police ask you questions,

455
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:06,080
just be honest and say

456
00:30:06,310 --> 00:30:07,480
what you can.

457
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:09,000
Which things can I say,

458
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:10,510
and which things can't I say?

459
00:30:10,510 --> 00:30:11,470
Say everything

460
00:30:11,590 --> 00:30:12,450
they can check.

461
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:14,180
And be honest.

462
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:18,230
