467
00:30:26,440 --> 00:30:28,150
Xiaowei told me

468
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:29,440
to be honest,

469
00:30:29,550 --> 00:30:30,760
answer whatever

470
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:31,650
