471
00:30:36,550 --> 00:30:39,000
Today, you drove the car
to divert the police.

472
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:40,160
That was his idea?

473
00:30:49,050 --> 00:30:50,210
You're

474
00:30:51,310 --> 00:30:52,640
Officer Zhou, right?

475
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:53,270
Yes.

476
00:30:53,830 --> 00:30:55,160
Can I ask you a question?

477
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:55,720
Sure.

478
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:57,200
I mean,

479
00:30:57,450 --> 00:30:58,760
did I break the law?

480
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:00,680
I... I'm asking about

481
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:02,640
the driving.

482
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,590
I don't know which part of my answer

483
00:31:04,590 --> 00:31:06,030
might have gotten me involved in this.

484
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:07,360
I can't guarantee that.

485
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,700
If you're not sure,

486
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:09,850
just ask the police.

487
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:13,830
Ask them.

488
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:17,200
If I did this thing,

489
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:19,160
would it be a crime?

490
00:31:25,070 --> 00:31:26,730
Driving itself
is not a crime.

491
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:29,030
But deliberately obstructing
a police investigation

492
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:30,240
is another matter.

493
00:31:33,590 --> 00:31:35,190
Then I'll tell you the truth.

494
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:37,240
Xiaowei told me to do it.

495
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:39,720
He told me to drive the car alone,

496
00:31:39,720 --> 00:31:41,480
and when I saw the intersection,

497
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,160
I should rush through.

498
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:42,920
He also reminded me

499
00:31:42,920 --> 00:31:43,780
to be careful,

500
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:44,690
don't get hurt,

501
00:31:45,030 --> 00:31:46,000
and don't crash the car.

502
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:48,310
Otherwise, I'll have to pay
the company back.

503
00:31:48,310 --> 00:31:49,350
The most important thing is,

504
00:31:49,350 --> 00:31:51,160
don't crash into other cars

505
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,440
or people.

506
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:56,030
As for what Xiaowei is up to,

507
00:31:57,030 --> 00:31:58,270
I really don't know.

508
00:31:58,750 --> 00:32:00,210
I'm just helping a friend.

509
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:01,240
He asked me to drive,

510
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:02,200
so I drove.

511
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,340
It wasn't intentional.

512
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:06,110
Earlier, you mentioned

513
00:32:06,510 --> 00:32:07,640
obstructing traffic...

514
00:32:07,640 --> 00:32:08,110
no,

515
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:11,180
obstructing the investigation, sorry.

516
00:32:12,590 --> 00:32:13,270
So,

517
00:32:14,590 --> 00:32:15,990
where did Xue Xiaowei go?

518
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:19,030
I don't know.

519
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,530
