554
00:33:58,830 --> 00:33:59,630
Chen Shuncai,

555
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:01,510
if you help him

556
00:34:01,550 --> 00:34:03,030
and obstruct the police investigation,

557
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:04,160
that's also a crime.

558
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:14,010
Xiaowei wouldn't kill anyone.

559
00:34:22,150 --> 00:34:23,500
[Video recording]

