South Cross Street at the same time.

567
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:43,540
Why is that?

568
00:34:43,710 --> 00:34:44,969
Do you know each other?

569
00:34:45,030 --> 00:34:45,760
Officer,

570
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:47,920
Er Gouzi, no,

571
00:34:50,550 --> 00:34:51,360
Chen Shuncai,

572
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:53,190
was raised by us.

573
00:34:55,230 --> 00:34:57,360
He's a relative of Xiaofang's family.

574
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,230
By bloodline,

575
00:35:00,100 --> 00:35:01,760
he should be her grandnephew.

576
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:04,230
His mother died young,

577
00:35:04,670 --> 00:35:05,800
the family was poor,

578
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:08,240
