581
00:35:13,030 --> 00:35:13,920
It was just

582
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:15,880
eating here,

583
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,410
sleeping there,

584
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:21,850
and he lived like that.

585
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:32,890
Do you know where Xue Xiaowei

586
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:34,320
and Xue Xiaoling are now?

587
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,760
Xue Xiaowei

588
00:35:44,150 --> 00:35:46,280
